(text "NOTE: no wires used - connectivity is via matching label names (valid KiCad practice)." (at 20.32 340.36 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 8baddcb6-50ab-5d39-b7d0-54417d7deaba))
(text "EC_GPIOx numbering is a local convenience mapping - see U4 pin_nets for actual STM32 pin/net cross-ref." (at 20.32 345.44 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 712d3b3d-6095-5ef8-9b1a-9de471453604))
(text "Anti-ghosting diodes for the keyboard matrix live on the separate MX ULP keyboard PCB." (at 20.32 351.79 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 1a73e688-7554-50fc-9018-c97cbf537d17))
(text "MCU_USB_DP/DM (PA12/PA11, OTG_FS device mode) are unrelated to the power-only USB-C PD sink ports." (at 20.32 358.14 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 29798bb2-42f5-5e2c-8b1d-ce70d51ff164))
(text "EC can assert Mu PWRBTN_N/RSTBTN_N; J16 case power is diode-isolated to Mu PWRBTN and charger QON." (at 20.32 364.49 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 40e3be7a-78e6-516f-8d73-f49a01726162))
(text "Hardware UARTs: VHF USART3 on PB10/PB11, UHF USART6 on PC6/PC7, GNSS USART1 on PA9/PA10." (at 20.32 369.57 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 1fd75630-94c8-5128-b1d2-fbb76f07afb8))
(text "AUX_DC_ADC monitors the screw-terminal wide-DC input so firmware can classify and current-limit that source." (at 20.32 375.92 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 1f96f8e3-fd56-5104-b8fd-26a0e9fd9059))
(text "PA7/PB0 are thermal ADCs; fan PWM uses timer-capable PE9/TIM1_CH1 and tach remains EC-owned." (at 20.32 383.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 3ab6abdf-22f1-5264-8b9e-23a61bfa48f8))
(text "The EC has no user GPIO header; all tinkering I/O is isolated to the integrated RP2350 maker domain." (at 20.32 391.16 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c186018a-1e01-507c-8ff6-6f2251e69dc0))
(text "U5 follows the TPS54202 3.3V table and runs from EC_AON_IN so source validation firmware can execute before arbitration." (at 20.32 398.78 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 6b2abd84-a8b3-5256-8f41-606d87a3de34))
(text "U5 EN is intentionally floated: TI specifies an internal pull-up that enables the converter when EN is open." (at 20.32 414.02 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c70680c9-6ccf-5800-b630-e92e4c5fae04))
(text "PE13 drives active-high MU_12V_ENABLE; PE14 reads MU_S0_HIGH; PE15 reads MU_12V_PG; PB1 reads TRACKPAD_FAULT_N." (at 20.32 406.4 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 29063ceb-3ecf-5e25-9488-5ef6d461ebe8))
